extends baseEmail

block content
    p Hi #{firstName},
    p From your Cyber Crime Report, we were able to get some potential cause of the incident 🎉🙏
    p We believe the potential cause of this incidence is a type of cyber Crime called #{cyberCrime}
    p Here are some tips to protect yourself against this kind of cyber crime
    ul
        each val, index in tips
            li= index + ': ' + val
    p If you need any help with creating a blog, please don't hesitate to contact me!
    p - Joshua Uzoagulu, CEO